<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mia AI – Trợ lý AI cho Spa & Salon Việt Nam</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --brand:  #6c3fff;
      --brand2: #9b5fff;
      --dark:   #0f0a1e;
      --text:   #1a1a2e;
      --muted:  #6b7280;
      --bg:     #f8f7ff;
      --card:   #ffffff;
      --border: #e8e4f8;
      --green:  #10b981;
      --gold:   #f59e0b;
    }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: white; overflow-x: hidden; }
    a { text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.96); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0 40px; height: 62px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; }
    .nav-logo .logo-icon {
      width: 34px; height: 34px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2));
      border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: white; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 900; font-style: italic;
    }
    .nav-logo .logo-text { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); }
    .nav-logo .logo-text span { color: var(--brand); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--brand); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
    .btn-ghost { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 8px; }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--bg); color: var(--brand); }
    .btn-trial {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2));
      color: white; padding: 9px 20px; border-radius: 9px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(108,63,255,.3);
    }
    .btn-trial:hover { opacity: .9; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 130px 20px 90px; text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0ebff 0%, #f8f7ff 50%, white 100%);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -200px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 700px; height: 700px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(108,63,255,.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
      background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 24px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(108,63,255,.1);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5.5vw, 64px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -.5px;
    }
    .hero h1 .grad {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), #c084fc);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .hero p { font-size: 17px; color: var(--muted); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.75; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2));
      color: white; padding: 15px 32px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(108,63,255,.35); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      border: 2px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; background: white;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--brand); color: var(--brand); }
    .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 40px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .h-stat { text-align: center; }
    .h-stat .num { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--brand); }
    .h-stat .lbl { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }

    /* ── BUSINESS TYPES ── */
    .biz-types { padding: 60px 20px; background: white; }
    .sec-label { text-align: center; color: var(--brand); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .sec-title { text-align: center; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -.3px; }
    .sec-sub   { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 44px; }
    .biz-grid { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6,1fr); gap: 16px; }
    .biz-card {
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 22px 12px; text-align: center; transition: all .2s; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .biz-card:hover { border-color: var(--brand); background: #f0ebff; transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(108,63,255,.12); }
    .biz-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .biz-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }

    /* ── WHY ── */
    .why { padding: 80px 20px; background: var(--bg); }
    .why-grid { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 28px; }
    .why-card {
      background: white; border-radius: 18px; padding: 32px 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); transition: box-shadow .2s;
    }
    .why-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(108,63,255,.1); }
    .why-num { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; color: #ede9fe; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text); }
    .why-card p  { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* ── FEATURES ── */
    .features { padding: 80px 20px; background: white; }
    .feat-wrap { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
    .feat-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .feat-item {
      display: flex; gap: 14px; padding: 18px 20px; border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid transparent; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s;
    }
    .feat-item.active, .feat-item:hover { background: var(--bg); border-color: var(--border); }
    .feat-item.active { border-color: var(--brand); background: #f0ebff; }
    .fi-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--bg); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 22px;
    }
    .feat-item.active .fi-icon { background: white; }
    .fi-text h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .fi-text p  { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
    /* Phone preview */
    .feat-phone { position: relative; }
    .feat-phone-wrap {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2));
      border-radius: 28px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(108,63,255,.3);
    }
    .mini-phone {
      background: #1c1c1e; border-radius: 32px; padding: 8px;
      max-width: 220px; margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #48484a, 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
    }
    .mini-screen { background: #ece5dd; border-radius: 26px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
    .mini-island { position: absolute; top: 6px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 70px; height: 20px; background: #000; border-radius: 12px; z-index: 5; }
    .mini-zalo-bar { background: #0068ff; color: white; padding: 32px 10px 8px; }
    .mini-zalo-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .mini-zav { width: 24px; height: 24px; background: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .mini-zlogo { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900; font-style: italic; color: #0068ff; }
    .mini-zname { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
    .mini-zsub  { font-size: 8px; opacity: .8; }
    .mini-body  { background: #f0f2f5; padding: 8px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; min-height: 200px; }
    .mm { max-width: 85%; padding: 6px 9px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 1.4; border-radius: 8px; }
    .mmb { background: white; align-self: flex-start; border-radius: 2px 8px 8px 8px; }
    .mmu { background: #d9f2ff; color: #003d99; align-self: flex-end; border-radius: 8px 2px 8px 8px; }
    .mmt { font-size: 8.5px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 1px; }
    .mmbtns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 3px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .mmbtn { background: #e8f0ff; border: 1px solid #99bbff; color: #0052cc; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 9.5px; }

    /* ── SOCIAL PROOF ── */
    .proof { padding: 72px 20px; background: var(--dark); color: white; }
    .proof .sec-label { color: #c084fc; }
    .proof .sec-title { color: white; }
    .proof .sec-sub { color: #9ca3af; }
    .proof-grid { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .proof-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 26px;
    }
    .proof-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .proof-text { font-size: 14px; color: #d1d5db; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 18px; font-style: italic; }
    .proof-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .proof-av { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }
    .proof-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: white; }
    .proof-role { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; }

    /* ── PRICING ── */
    .pricing { padding: 80px 20px; background: white; }
    .plans { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 22px; align-items: start; }
    .plan { border-radius: 20px; border: 2px solid var(--border); background: white; overflow: hidden; transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; }
    .plan:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .plan.hot {
      border-color: var(--brand);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0ebff 0%, white 30%);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(108,63,255,.2);
    }
    .plan.hot:hover { transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-5px); }
    .plan.elite { border-color: #7c3aed; }
    .plan-top { padding: 28px 26px 22px; }
    .plan-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .badge-free { background: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; }
    .badge-hot  { background: #ede9fe; color: var(--brand); }
    .badge-elite{ background: #1e1b4b; color: #a5b4fc; }
    .plan-name  { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .plan-desc  { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .plan-price { font-size: 38px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--text); line-height: 1; }
    .plan-price span { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--muted); }
    .plan-price-note { font-size: 12px; color: #bbb; margin-top: 4px; }
    .plan-div { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 26px; }
    .plan-feats { padding: 20px 26px 26px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .pf { display: flex; gap: 10px; font-size: 13.5px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.45; }
    .pf .ic { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1px; }
    .pf .ic.purple { color: var(--brand); }
    .pf small { display: block; font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 1px; }
    .plan-cta-wrap { padding: 0 26px 28px; }
    .plan-btn { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 13px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }
    .btn-free { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .btn-hot  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2)); color: white; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(108,63,255,.3); }
    .btn-elite{ background: #1e1b4b; color: white; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 90px 20px; text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b 0%, #4c1d95 50%, #6c3fff 100%);
      color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-section::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -100px;
      width: 400px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: -.3px; }
    .cta-section p  { opacity: .8; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-cta-main { background: white; color: var(--brand); padding: 15px 32px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.2); }
    .btn-cta-outline { border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4); color: white; padding: 15px 28px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; }
    .cta-note { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 13px; opacity: .6; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer { background: #0a0814; color: #4b5563; padding: 36px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
    footer .f-logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    footer .f-logo span { color: var(--brand2); }
    footer p { color: #4b5563; margin-top: 6px; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .biz-grid   { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); }
      .plans      { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .proof-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .feat-wrap  { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .why-grid   { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      nav .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav { padding: 0 16px; }
      .biz-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
      .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <div class="logo-icon">M</div>
    <div class="logo-text">Mia<span>AI</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#features">Tính năng</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Bảng giá</a>
    <a href="#reviews">Khách hàng</a>
    <a href="#contact">Liên hệ</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <a href="#" class="btn-ghost">Đăng nhập</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-trial">Dùng thử miễn phí</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">🤖 Trợ lý AI số 1 cho ngành làm đẹp Việt Nam</div>
  <h1>Tự động hóa Spa & Salon<br>với <span class="grad">Trợ lý AI</span></h1>
  <p>Khách đặt lịch 24/7 qua Zalo & WhatsApp — trợ lý AI tư vấn, xác nhận, nhắc lịch tự động. Bạn chỉ cần tập trung phục vụ.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">🚀 Dùng thử miễn phí 30 ngày</a>
    <a href="#features" class="btn-secondary">▶ Xem demo</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="num">500+</div><div class="lbl">Spa & Salon đang dùng</div></div>
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="num">24/7</div><div class="lbl">Nhận đặt lịch tự động</div></div>
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="num">< 1s</div><div class="lbl">Thời gian phản hồi</div></div>
    <div class="h-stat"><div class="num">0đ</div><div class="lbl">Chi phí dùng thử</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BUSINESS TYPES -->
<section class="biz-types">
  <div class="sec-label">Phù hợp cho</div>
  <div class="sec-title">Mọi loại hình làm đẹp</div>
  <div class="sec-sub">Từ spa cao cấp đến tiệm nail nhỏ — trợ lý AI hoạt động ngay</div>
  <div class="biz-grid">
    <div class="biz-card"><div class="biz-icon">💆</div><div class="biz-name">Spa</div></div>
    <div class="biz-card"><div class="biz-icon">✂️</div><div class="biz-name">Hair Salon</div></div>
    <div class="biz-card"><div class="biz-icon">💅</div><div class="biz-name">Nail</div></div>
    <div class="biz-card"><div class="biz-icon">🪒</div><div class="biz-name">Barber</div></div>
    <div class="biz-card"><div class="biz-icon">🧖</div><div class="biz-name">Thẩm mỹ</div></div>
    <div class="biz-card"><div class="biz-icon">🦷</div><div class="biz-name">Nha khoa</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY -->
<section class="why">
  <div class="sec-label">Tại sao chọn MiaAI</div>
  <div class="sec-title">3 lý do chủ salon tin dùng</div>
  <div class="sec-sub" style="margin-bottom:44px"></div>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-num">01</div>
      <h3>Không cần kỹ thuật</h3>
      <p>Setup xong trong 1 ngày làm việc. Không cần biết lập trình, không cần server — chúng tôi lo tất cả, bạn chỉ cần dùng.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-num">02</div>
      <h3>AI hiểu khách như người thật</h3>
      <p>Không phải bot bấm nút cứng nhắc. Trợ lý AI hiểu ngôn ngữ tự nhiên, gợi ý dịch vụ, nhớ sở thích khách quen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-num">03</div>
      <h3>Tăng doanh thu tự động</h3>
      <p>Tự gửi khuyến mãi, nhắc khách lâu không quay lại, thu thập đánh giá — tất cả chạy tự động không cần thao tác thủ công.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="sec-label">Tính năng</div>
  <div class="sec-title">Trợ lý làm được gì?</div>
  <div class="sec-sub" style="margin-bottom:50px">Tất cả những gì cần để vận hành salon hiệu quả</div>
  <div class="feat-wrap">
    <div class="feat-list">
      <div class="feat-item active">
        <div class="fi-icon">💬</div>
        <div class="fi-text">
          <h4>Đặt lịch qua Zalo & WhatsApp</h4>
          <p>Khách nhắn tin bất cứ lúc nào — trợ lý xác nhận lịch tức thì, không cần gọi điện.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-item">
        <div class="fi-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="fi-text">
          <h4>AI tư vấn dịch vụ thông minh</h4>
          <p>Hiểu nhu cầu, gợi ý dịch vụ phù hợp, upsell combo tự động theo lịch sử khách hàng.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-item">
        <div class="fi-icon">🔔</div>
        <div class="fi-text">
          <h4>Nhắc lịch & giảm no-show</h4>
          <p>Tự động nhắc trước 2 tiếng và 30 phút. Giảm tỉ lệ khách quên lịch xuống dưới 5%.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-item">
        <div class="fi-icon">🎁</div>
        <div class="fi-text">
          <h4>Marketing tự động</h4>
          <p>Gửi khuyến mãi sinh nhật, nhắc khách lâu không quay lại, phát voucher cho khách quen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-item">
        <div class="fi-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="fi-text">
          <h4>Báo cáo & phân tích</h4>
          <p>Dashboard thống kê doanh thu, khách hàng, dịch vụ phổ biến — realtime trên điện thoại.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-phone">
      <div class="feat-phone-wrap">
        <div class="mini-phone">
